# Article section iteration agents (ieee_journal.tex → src/sec/*.tex)
kind: article_sections
description: >-
  Per-section rd-agent / adk-ralph YAML specs for iterative improvement of LaTeX sections
  after the NIST trustworthy-AI questionnaire battery (`scripts/run_nist_llm_evaluation.py`)
  and recorded scores (`output/results/nist_quiz_scores.json`). Not a graded homework CONFIG;
  optional for rd-agent-mcp validate-tests (may ignore unknown roots).
ieee_driver: src/ieee_journal.tex
section_glob: src/sec/*.tex
workflow_doc: test_cases/article_sections/README.md
nist_eval_driver: scripts/run_nist_llm_evaluation.py
nist_rubric_emitter: scripts/emit_nist_rubric_table.py
nist_eval_json: output/results/nist_eval_latest.json
nist_scores_json: output/results/nist_quiz_scores.json
nist_rubric_tex: output/results/nist_rubric_table.tex
homework_pdf: homework-assignment.pdf
nist_prompts_py: scripts/nist_quiz_prompts.py
